title: Virginia Tech recruiting: 3-star ATH Dante Lovett commits to Hokies' 2023 class - The Athletic
content: Virginia Tech recruiting: 3-star ATH Dante Lovett commits to Hokies' 2023 class  The Athletic
description: Three-star Hyattsville, Md., athlete Dante Lovett announced his commitment to Virginia Tech's recruiting Class of 2023 on Sunday.
